David Rowland Takes 36% Stake in Hamleys Toy Store, Times Says

-- B y   G a v i n   F i n c h
-- 
2011-05-29T12:18:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-29/david-rowland-takes-36-stake-in-hamleys-toy-store-times-says.html
David Rowland of Rowland Capital and
his son Jonathan Rowland have bought a 36 percent stake in
London toy store Hamleys Plc, the  Sunday Times  reported, without
saying where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Gavin Finch in London at 
 gfinch@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
